  "text": "<html>\r\n    <head>\r\n    <style>\r\n        .unselectable {\r\n          -webkit-user-select: none;\r\n          -webkit-touch-callout: none;\r\n          -moz-user-select: none;\r\n          -ms-user-select: none;\r\n          user-select: none;\r\n        }\r\n      <\/style>\r\n      <\/head>\r\n\r\n<body class=\"unselectable\">\r\n \r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">VERB QUESTIONS; &lsquo;WAS&rsquo; AND &lsquo;WHEN&rsquo;<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">These are the past simple forms of the verb &lsquo;to be&rsquo;. Generally, &lsquo;was&rsquo; is used with singular pronouns (one subject), and &lsquo;were&rsquo; is used with plural pronouns (more than one subject), but the pronoun &lsquo;you&rsquo; is an exception!<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">WAS<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">is usually used with the pronouns<\/span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&lsquo;I&rsquo;, &lsquo;she&rsquo;, &lsquo;he&rsquo;<\/span><\/em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">, and<\/span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&lsquo;it&rsquo;<\/span><\/em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">.<\/span><br><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">WERE<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">is usually used with pronouns<\/span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&lsquo;you&rsquo;, &lsquo;we&rsquo;<\/span><\/em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">, and<\/span><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&lsquo;they&rsquo;<\/span><\/em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">(See the information just before and after &lsquo;USE 2&rsquo; below, for more information about the use of the pronouns &lsquo;you&rsquo; and &lsquo;I&rsquo;.)<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">[Tweet &ldquo;WAS is usually used with the pronouns &lsquo;I&rsquo;, &lsquo;she&rsquo;, &lsquo;he&rsquo;, and &lsquo;it&rsquo;. &ldquo;]<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Past simple<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Some basic sentence examples:<\/span><\/p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:9.6pt; margin-bottom:8pt; padding-left:3.9pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">I was<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">married for 5 years.<\/span><\/em><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:9.6pt; margin-bottom:8pt; padding-left:3.9pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">She was<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">unwell last week.<\/span><\/em><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:9.6pt; margin-bottom:8pt; padding-left:3.9pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">It was<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">not my fault!<\/span><\/em><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:9.6pt; margin-bottom:8pt; padding-left:3.9pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">We were<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">worried about the test results.<\/span><\/em><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:9.6pt; margin-bottom:8pt; padding-left:3.9pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">They were<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">busy working all day yesterday.<\/span><\/em><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:9.6pt; margin-bottom:8pt; padding-left:3.9pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">You were<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">supposed to help me.<\/span><\/em><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">However, there are exceptions to this rule!<\/span><br><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Firstly, as I mentioned before, even though &lsquo;you&rsquo; is a singular pronoun it is used with WERE.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-bottom:8pt; text-indent:-36pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt; list-style-position:inside; -aw-list-padding-sml:3.9pt;\"><span style=\"font:7pt 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">You were<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">asleep when he rang.<\/span><\/em><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-bottom:8pt; text-indent:-36pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt; list-style-position:inside; -aw-list-padding-sml:3.9pt;\"><span style=\"font:7pt 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">Where<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">were you<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">yesterday?<\/span><\/em><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-bottom:8pt; text-indent:-36pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt; list-style-position:inside; -aw-list-padding-sml:3.9pt;\"><span style=\"font:7pt 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">Whom<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">were you<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">talking to?<\/span><\/em><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">[&ldquo;WERE is usually used with pronouns &lsquo;you&rsquo;, &lsquo;we&rsquo;, and &lsquo;they&rsquo;.&rdquo;]<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Past subjunctive as a conditional<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Secondly, the pronoun &lsquo;I&rsquo; can be used with WERE as a conditional as well as with WAS. WERE is the past subjunctive of the present verb &lsquo;to be&rsquo;, meaning it expresses hope, possibility or supposition rather than stating a fact.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:9.6pt; margin-bottom:8pt; padding-left:3.9pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">If I were<\/span><\/em><\/strong><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">you, I wouldn&rsquo;t touch that.<\/span><\/em><br><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">(I&rsquo;m not you, it&rsquo;s hypothetical &ndash; used for the present or future)<\/span><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:9.6pt; margin-bottom:8pt; padding-left:3.9pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">If I were<\/span><\/em><\/strong><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">a multi-billionaire, I would rid the world of poverty.<\/span><\/em><br><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">(I&rsquo;m not a multi-billionaire, it&rsquo;s hypothetical &ndash; used for the present or future)<\/span><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:9.6pt; margin-bottom:8pt; padding-left:3.9pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">If I were<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">in his shoes, I would accept their offer.<\/span><br><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">(I&rsquo;m not him or in his position, it&rsquo;s hypothetical &ndash; used for the present and future)<\/span><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:9.6pt; margin-bottom:8pt; padding-left:3.9pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">If I was<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">rude to you yesterday, I&rsquo;m very sorry.<\/span><\/em><br><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">(The condition is unclear, but it is presumed to have been true in the past)<\/span><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:9.6pt; margin-bottom:8pt; padding-left:3.9pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">If I was<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">annoying you last night, I&rsquo;m sorry. I was in a bad mood.<\/span><\/em><br><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">(The condition is unclear, but it is presumed to have been true in the past)<\/span><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:9.6pt; margin-bottom:8pt; padding-left:3.9pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">If I was<\/span><\/em><\/strong><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">healthier<\/span><\/em><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">,<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">I probably would have been able to win the race.<\/span><\/em><br><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">(The condition is unclear, but it is presumed to have been a possibility of being true in the past)<\/span><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">UNN PUTME Example<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">He behaves as if he ____a governor.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">A. is B. was C. were D. are<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">(Were, 2018\/2019, no 6)<\/span><\/em><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Past continuous \/ past simple<\/span><\/em><\/strong><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Remember that in Past Simple, a specific time is used to show when an action began or finished. In Past Continuous (Progressive), a specific time only interrupts the action.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Interrupted action in the past<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">[subject 1 + WAS\/WERE + verb + ing + WHEN + subject 2 + past simple verb]<\/span><br><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Use Past Continuous to indicate when a longer action in the past was interrupted, usually by a shorter action that occurs (Past Simple).<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Here are some examples:<\/span><\/p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-bottom:8pt; text-indent:-36pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt; list-style-position:inside; -aw-list-padding-sml:8.4pt;\"><span style=\"font:7pt 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">She was studying when<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">he called.<\/span><\/em><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-bottom:8pt; text-indent:-36pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt; list-style-position:inside; -aw-list-padding-sml:8.4pt;\"><span style=\"font:7pt 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">He was cooking when<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">the phone rang.<\/span><\/em><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-bottom:8pt; text-indent:-36pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt; list-style-position:inside; -aw-list-padding-sml:8.4pt;\"><span style=\"font:7pt 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">They were shopping when<\/span><\/em><\/strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">they heard an explosion.<\/span><\/em><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-bottom:8pt; text-indent:-36pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt; list-style-position:inside; -aw-list-padding-sml:8.4pt;\"><span style=\"font:7pt 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">We were dancing when<\/span><\/em><\/strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">the power went out.<\/span><\/em><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-bottom:8pt; text-indent:-36pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt; list-style-position:inside; -aw-list-padding-sml:8.4pt;\"><span style=\"font:7pt 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">I was listening to music when<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">the doorbell rang.<\/span><\/em><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-left:36pt; margin-bottom:8pt; text-indent:-36pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"width:36pt; text-indent:0pt; display:inline-block;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">A series of parallel actions<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">A series of parallel actions can be used to describe the atmosphere at a particular time in the past.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:22.5pt; margin-bottom:8pt; text-indent:-18pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt; list-style-position:inside; -aw-list-padding-sml:3.9pt;\"><span style=\"font:7pt 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">When I walked into my house, my husband<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">was watching TV<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">, the<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">baby was crying<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">, my<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">son was playing<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">computer games, and the<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">dog was barking<\/span><\/em><\/strong><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">in the garden!<\/span><\/em><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin-left:22.5pt; margin-bottom:8pt; text-indent:-18pt; font-family:serif; font-size:10pt; list-style-position:inside; -aw-list-padding-sml:3.9pt;\"><span style=\"font:7pt 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">When I stepped into the office, my<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">boss was shouting<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">at someone on the phone, his<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">secretary was running<\/span><\/em><\/strong><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">towards his office, my<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">assistant was printing<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">a document, and all the<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">telephones were<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">constantly<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">ringing<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt;\">!<\/span><\/em><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Active and passive<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Sentences can be active or passive. Most sentences are active, where the subject is doing the action and the object is receiving the action. The subject and object can be swapped around to change a sentence from active to passive.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Active<\/span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&ndash; The professor<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">was teaching<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">his students.<\/span><\/em><br><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Passive<\/span><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&ndash; The students<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">were being taught by<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">the professor.<\/span><\/em><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Active<\/span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&ndash; Jenny<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">was making tea for<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">her friends.<\/span><\/em><br><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Passive<\/span><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&ndash; Tea<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">was being made by<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Jenny for her friends.<\/span><\/em><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Active<\/span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&ndash;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Her brother was<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">hugging her.<\/span><\/em><br><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Passive<\/span><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&ndash;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">She was being hugged by<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">her brother.<\/span><\/em><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Summary<\/span><\/em><\/strong><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">These words are used differently in sentences, so it&rsquo;s important to know when to use were vs. was.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Was is used in the first- and third-person singular past. It is used for statements of fact.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Were<\/span><\/em><\/strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;is used in the second person singular and plural and first and third person plural. It is used in the subjunctive mood to indicate unreal or hypothetical statements. The words if and wish usually indicate the subjunctive mood.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">UNN PUTME&nbsp;<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">1. My friend and classmate ______ present when the girls insulted me.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">A. were. B. is C was. D. are<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">(C. Was (2011\/2012, no 7)<\/span><\/em><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2. The mechanic did not tell me the brakes ... bad A. were B. are C. is D. was.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">(were)<\/span><\/em><br><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">3. 15. If I _____ in Udenta&rsquo;s position, I would go into politics.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">A. am B. was C. were D. be<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">(were)<\/span><\/em><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">(Subjective Mood: This is another test on the Subjunctive Mood Note that whenever demand, resolution, recommendation, wish, suggestion or prayer is involved in a sentence, the verb of the sentence should be plural, whether the subject is singular or plural).<\/span><\/em><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">JAMB Example<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">1. The mechanic did not tell me the brakes ... bad A. were B. are C. is D. was.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; font-size:12pt;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">(were)<\/span><\/em><br><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<\/body>\r\n\r\n<\/html>",
  "chapIndex": "VERB QUESTIONS; \u2018WAS\u2019 AND \u2018WHEN\u2019"
}